          "arabic": "لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ",
          "transliteration": "Lam yalid wa lam yulad",
          "translation": "He neither begets nor was begotten",
          "audioFile": "https://everyayah.com/data/Alafasy_128kbps/112003.mp3",
          "audioSource": "everyayah"
        },
        {
          "id": "ikhlas-4",
