          "translation": "All greetings, prayers and good things are for Allah",
          "audioFile": "",
          "audioSource": "elevenlabs"
        },
        {
          "id": "tashahhud-2",
          "arabic": "السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِيُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ",
          "transliteration": "Assalamu 'alaika ayyuhan-nabiyyu wa rahmatullahi wa barakatuh",
          "translation": "Peace be upon you, O Prophet, and the mercy of Allah and His blessings",
          "audioFile": "",
          "audioSource": "elevenlabs"
        },
        {
          "id": "tashahhud-3",
          "arabic": "السَّلَامُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَىٰ عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ",
          "transliteration": "Assalamu 'alaina wa 'ala 'ibadillahis-saliheen",
          "translation": "Peace be upon us and upon the righteous servants of Allah",
          "audioFile": "",
          "audioSource": "elevenlabs"
        },
        {
          "id": "tashahhud-4",
          "arabic": "أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَٰهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ",
          "transliteration": "Ash-hadu alla ilaha illallah, wa ash-hadu anna Muhammadan 'abduhu wa rasuluh",
          "translation": "I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and Muhammad is His servant and messenger",
          "audioFile": "",
          "audioSource": "elevenlabs"
        }
      ]
